{"tid":1021600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"35歲魯蛇徵女友...要求「C奶+海溝型下體」　網見本尊怒了！","createTime":"2019-02-14T10:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T13:45:06.000Z","uid":212399,"like":29,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5b7b7d8e526c5edb506cf10abcf6fc7634db52","tid":1021600,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3896/d3896207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3896%2Fd3896207.jpg&h=fc31aafe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲魯蛇長這樣。（圖／<a href=\"http://翻攝自mumsnet.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BF%BB%E6%94%9D%E8%87%AAmumsnet.com&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=6b81d95d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">翻攝自mumsnet.com</a>，下同）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n澳洲網路近日一篇徵女友文在「<a href=\"http://mumsnet.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmumsnet.com&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=b7bebcd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mumsnet.com</a>」上引起熱議，文內不但要求超多，原PO更大膽要求對方一定要有「C罩杯」和「海溝型陰道」（innie vagina）。此文一發，立刻引來網友撻伐，覺得他超不尊重女性。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，一名自稱是35歲的澳洲男子，發布一則徵女友文至Facebook，他寫道「女方要是白人，年齡要在19-23歲，身高不能高於155公分，體重要在43-47kg之間，且要有工作、執照，有車更好，還要經常上健身房。」此外，他更誇張要求女生要有C罩杯以上，還要有「海溝型陰道」（innie vagina），臉上不能穿環，身上也不能有「廉價低俗的刺青」。<br />\n這還不夠，原PO更於文末加碼補充，「對方要願意搬到坎培拉（Canberra）陪我生活，要有一個良好的個性和幽默感，永遠不會生氣，當我整個假日都不回家時，也不要沒有安全感。」他同時附上自己經過濾鏡修飾、頭戴一雙貓耳朵，對著鏡頭幾眉弄眼的自拍照。<br />\n這篇超高標準的「徵女友」文一發，馬上引起網友撻伐，並瘋傳這篇文章，大罵該男「有嚴重的性別歧視且不尊重女性」，不少網友也紛紛留言諷刺「難怪他35歲還單身」、「好失敗的人，女生只會更討厭他」、「祝他永遠找不到女友」。但也有網友認為，這篇文章應該是他前女友發的，想警告大家他是怎麼樣的人。<br />\n「海溝型陰道」（innie vagina）指大陰唇包覆著小陰唇，無外翻、外露；相反則為「火山型陰道」(outtie vagina) 指女性的小陰唇大於大陰唇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190214/1378043.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190214%2F1378043.htm&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=11d3f75f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190214/1378043.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a28f6ecc705c1dbb45bde0c732318b88926c5e65","tid":1021600,"uid":137997,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd59d8da1d8b394093f3faf4c14ccfa0bf97bc9f","tid":1021600,"uid":212399,"like":367,"dislike":2,"score":365,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"鬼佬連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52547582fbb9ba2d5728178e35ed85f69ca04794","tid":1021600,"uid":1049,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"點驗貨係咪一線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356e900a150d6e4af4c60afc5fa0db5de3b8106d","tid":1021600,"uid":53186,"like":226,"dislike":3,"score":223,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"35歲都咁多要求,抵佢冇囡"},{"pid":"7117cda4d4aa006da8ae01a6607801fbea54b88f","tid":1021600,"uid":51932,"like":71,"dislike":5,"score":66,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"海溝型陰道<br />\n<br />\n有冇圖研究下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46291b544999321eeba8dce4e7dac3f48fac35b","tid":1021600,"uid":1049,"like":104,"dislike":0,"score":104,"quote":{"pid":"356e900a150d6e4af4c60afc5fa0db5de3b8106d","tid":1021600,"uid":53186,"like":226,"dislike":3,"score":223,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"35歲都咁多要求,抵佢冇囡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"佢係李澤楷都可以既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa